arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: This collection is arranged into the following series:

list.item: Series I. Trade Mission Briefing Binders, 1991;

did.unittitle: Series I. Trade Mission Briefing Binders, 1991 (Acc. 35586).

scopecontent.p: Trade Mission Briefing Binders, 1991, are housed in 2 boxes. These binders document trade missions to both Europe (1991 June) and Asia (1991 October). The European Trade Mission traveled to Belgium, Great Britain, Germany and Poland; and the Asian Trade Mission traveled to Hong Kong, Japan and Korea. The briefing binders include scheduling information (events, participants, travel logistics), prelimary information (overview of mission and country), background information for meetings (participants and issues), and general background information (new articles, business reports, companies in Virginia, overview of trade and investment in Virginia).

News Summaries, 1990-1993, are housed in X boxes and are arranged chronologically. These news summaries consist of photocopies of news articles of interest that were distributed to the Governor and his staff on a nearly daily basis. Handwritten subject topics can be found in the upper right corner of each article.
